Subject: [PATCH 33/58] ENGR00283412 fix only audio output from Wfdsink if
 press home key

override  the onStop() and  onRestart() method
to stop Wfdsink when press Home key.

Signed-off-by: ZhongWen <b47623@freescale.com>
---
